{"tid":1905661,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠請入","createTime":"2020-03-01T11:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T15:42:10.000Z","uid":139117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca33d2b9b6a829f0fbfe0992d40e84404f7a356","tid":1905661,"uid":139117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"林奠係fb表示<br />\n香港的防控疫情工作堅持以科學為證及理據為本，以目前共95宗確診數字看，措施是有效的。<br />\n <br />\n你個八婆我同你講<br />\n香港之所以感染率低 <br />\n係因為我哋係全世界最唔信任中國嘅既地方 <br />\n由佢一爆出依單野我哋就搶口罩瘋狂文宣高度戒備 <br />\n有今日嘅數字都係全賴我地香港人嘅努力 <br />\n你wfh就咪撚喺度搶功勞 <br />\n之後笑我哋嘅其他國家而家賴哂野 <br />\n都係因為佢哋信中國話低死亡率 <br />\n所以香港人我地要繼續團結 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50f642adda1d57fc16e6309dd3e4d5a1beda3dc","tid":1905661,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wr0x1Ne.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwr0x1Ne.jpg&h=59167e6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8ee6a82d79e68fe9d68f4212fc2beec6902fce1","tid":1905661,"uid":139117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T11:54:11.000Z","msg":"Sorry for太撚激動1999"},{"pid":"57c0998148842f80f89e2cf77a037fedded9fc1c","tid":1905661,"uid":139117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T12:15:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"802299ebfe1180cf2358e434c0f8eedfd35a3550","tid":1905661,"uid":139117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e180ce12fd47e6b225279c5f9163cc45c53044fb","tid":1905661,"uid":139117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4927647395f80fc777fa640b0ee1edc5bf44cca5","tid":1905661,"uid":139117,"like":0,"dis